      warningBox: "Events that prevent, or threaten to prevent, safe care — an evacuation, a sustained outage affecting care, an outbreak — engage gov-005's notification duties to the regulator, and commissioner and family communication runs alongside, honest about what has happened and what is being done. Continuity failures compounded by silence become scandals; the same failures handled with candour become case studies."
