  statement: "Everything else this organisation promises — consent, involvement, dignity, safety — runs through communication. A person who cannot make themselves understood, or cannot understand what is happening to them, is cut off from their own care whatever the care plan says. Communication support is therefore not a specialism bolted onto care; it is the medium care travels in, and every member of staff is a communication worker whether they think of themselves that way or not.",
